title: NASCAR: Kenseth adamant Logano wrecked him intentionally
text: Photo: Butch Dill, AP NASCAR Sprint Cup Series driver Matt Kenseth talks with crew members during practice for Sunday's NASCAR auto race at Talladega Superspeedway Friday, Oct. 23, 2015, in Talladega, Ala.. NASCAR Sprint Cup Series driver Matt Kenseth talks with crew... TALLADEGA, Ala. (AP) — Joey Logano chalked up contact with Matt Kenseth as aggressive racing for a win.
